00:01:23.670 --> 00:01:25.870
NARRATOR: Since the
program began in 2003,

00:01:25.870 --> 00:01:29.890
80% of the town's garbage gets
recycled, reused, or composted.

00:01:29.890 --> 00:01:31.310
The rest goes to a landfill.

00:01:31.310 --> 00:01:35.511
But by 2020, the goal is
to be 100% zero waste.

00:01:35.511 --> 00:01:37.010
