understanding of the people.

00:02:17.920 --> 00:02:21.340
Of course, when they
had to separate garbage

00:02:21.340 --> 00:02:26.236
into 34 categories, which is
massive, it's really tough.

00:02:29.700 --> 00:02:32.720
NARRATOR: Residents must
washed, clean, sort, and then

00:02:32.720 --> 00:02:35.480
bring all of the materials to
the city's recycling center

00:02:35.480 --> 00:02:38.310
where monitors such
as Kazuyuki Kiyohara

00:02:38.310 --> 00:02:40.567
make sure it's
being done properly.

00:02:40.567 --> 00:02:42.260
